<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verification Code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        p {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            color: #2563eb;
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 32px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">NextGen School</div>
        <h1>Verification Code</h1>
        <p>Hello <%= name %>, please use the code below to verify your account or reset your password. This code will expire in 2 minutes.</p>
        <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
        <p>If you didn't request this code, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 NextGen School Management System. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
